## Database (Neon)
## Get these from: https://console.neon.tech/
## Runtime (pooled): hostname contains `-pooler`
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@ep-xxxx-pooler.c-2.region.aws.neon.tech/dbname?sslmode=require&channel_binding=require"
## Prisma migrations/Studio (direct): hostname does NOT contain `-pooler`
DATABASE_URL_DIRECT="postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@ep-xxxx.c-2.region.aws.neon.tech/dbname?sslmode=require&channel_binding=require"

## Cross-app base URLs for local dev via Caddy (:3200)
PB_PUBLIC_BASE_URL="http://localhost:3200"
PB_PORTAL_BASE_URL="http://localhost:3200/portal"
PB_STAFF_BASE_URL="http://localhost:3200/staff"
PB_API_BASE_URL="http://localhost:3200/api"

## Cloudflare R2 Storage Configuration
## Get these from: Cloudflare Dashboard > R2 > Manage R2 API Tokens
R2_ACCOUNT_ID=your-cloudflare-account-id
R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your-r2-access-key-id
R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your-r2-secret-access-key
R2_BUCKET_NAME=your-bucket-name
## Optional: if your bucket is public, set this to return a clickable URL after upload
# R2_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=https://pub-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx.r2.dev
## Optional: token to protect the upload endpoint (recommended for production)
# R2_UPLOAD_TOKEN=your-secure-random-token
